Convenient Utilities

  {{{./apidocs/com/jcabi/log/Logger.html}<<<Logger>>>}}
  is a convenient wrapper around {{{http://www.slf4j.org/}slf4j}}
  (don't forget to include one of
  {{{http://www.slf4j.org/manual.html#binding}slf4j bindings}}
  into your project):

+--
import com.jcabi.log.Logger;
class Foo {
  void bar(int value) {
    Logger.debug(this, "method bar(%d) was called", value);
  }
}
+--

  Read about {{{./decors.html}decors}}.

  Don't forget to include <<<jcabi-log>>> dependency into your project:

+--
<dependency>
  <groupId>com.jcabi</groupId>
  <artifactId>jcabi-log</artifactId>
  <version>${releasedVersion}</version>
</dependency>
+--

